snippet.title: Overwatch 2 | Season 8: Call of the Hunt | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Overwatch 2 Season 8: Call of the Hunt launches Dec 5!
Charge in guns blazin’ with the newest tank Hero, Mauga
Unlock new Beast Hunter-themed skins in an all-new Battle Pass
Go big or go home in the Battle of the Beasts event mode
Flex your hardware with all-new Weapon Skins
Celebrate Winter Wonderland with returning game modes and the new Winter Fair Event Pass
Traverse 5 new courses in Hero Mastery
Bring in the Year of the Dragon during our Lunar New Year event!
Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!

_
